<br>
Man, I can't fucking believe how badly this patch fucked up Necro's. When 3/4 of your soloing ways are fucked up so bad, that its impossible to solo efficiently anymore, its utter bull shit. For those that have no idea what the hell I'm talking about, heres some background. Necro's solo in 4 different ways by : root/dotting, charm killing, fear kiting, and aggro kiting. Which one is still alive? Root/Dotting! The most ineffecient way to kill a fucking mob, because it wastes extra mana and time. <br>
<br>
Now what happened to charm killing? Should you even ask? Look at that patch message. If that looks like ebonics to you, well here I am to explain what it means. No negative magic modifier = you can't do fucking shit in PoP. Mobs in PoP were designed w/ extremely high resists, therefor the spells were designed with negative (lure type) modifiers. Now when you take that away, it means absolute a piece of shit. WoT (Words of Terris, our Necro charm) is now being called a waste of time (hey, look how it fits so perfectly). Now if they had just applied a higher exp penalty w/ charm killing, fuck I wouldn't care, because I admit...it was over powered. Now look at it, I wasted 40 minutes in CoD attempting to charm kill, and best effect I got was a 20 second charm and rest were resists. Way to go on fucking that up. <br>
<br>
Now Aggro kiting, as known as, dumping as much dots to piss off a mob and kite it around while your pet beats it up. Simple concept, expect what? You guessed it, we got stupid pets that taunt like wizards landing 6k crit nukes 10 times in a row. Way to go on fucking up our best effecient way to solo. <br>
<br>
We all know that fear kiting was long dead when PoP came out, but that was ok, we found other ways to get around, but for a Lv 1 - 55/60 Necro, that shit was the only way to kill anything in Norrath. The point of Necro pets being a piece of shit was because we can fear kite... also its the only way we can solo at lower levels. Now that you have implemented that pathing fix, hey, the mob now travels in a linear line and no longer sways back and forth. What does that mean now? It means it travels like 10 fucking miles before it fucking dies and also means add's because it's pathing so damn far. Now this doesn't bother me one bit because im past the era of fear kiting, but goddamn, you just screw the newbie era.<br>
<br>
I'm sort of relieved in the fact that I've grinded out all the essential AA's that I need, so that soloing would be the last thing I need to think about, but this does effect shit as far as farming or whatever else I do to keep myself busy with. And this does effect other Necro's that are working actively toward their lvl/aa goals, and is a huge impact upon them. Hell, they may fix it one day, but until then, fuck you Sony for implementing the most stupidest and buggiest patch of the year.<br>
